Interface IBlogMLCommonObject

Allows an object to implement common Web Log Markup Language (BlogML) entity information by representing a set of properties, methods, indexers and events common to BlogML syndication resources.

Namespace: Argotic.Syndication.Specialized
Assembly: Argotic.Core.dll

ApprovalStatus

Gets or sets the approval status of the web log entity.

Declaration
BlogMLApprovalStatus ApprovalStatus { get; set; }
Property Value
Type Description
BlogMLApprovalStatus

An BlogMLApprovalStatus enumeration value that represents whether the web log entity was approved to be publicly available. The default value is None, which indicates that no approval status information was specified.

CreatedOn

Gets or sets a date-time indicating when the web log entity was created.

Declaration
DateTime CreatedOn { get; set; }
Property Value
Type Description
System.DateTime

A System.DateTime that indicates an instant in time associated with an event early in the life cycle of the web log entity. The default value is System.DateTime.MinValue, which indicates that no creation date-time was provided.
Remarks

The System.DateTime should be provided in Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).

LastModifiedOn

Gets or sets a date-time indicating when the web log entity was last modified.

Declaration
DateTime LastModifiedOn { get; set; }
Property Value
Type Description
System.DateTime

A System.DateTime that indicates the most recent instant in time when the web log entity was modified in a way the publisher considers significant. The default value is System.DateTime.MinValue, which indicates that no modification date-time was provided.
Remarks

The System.DateTime should be provided in Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).
